room_title: Escape room "Mirror Mirror" by Brainstorm Escape Room Bonita Springs in Fort Myers
room_description: Traveling through the wilderness, you and your friends stumble upon an ancient castle. Curiosity sets in and you want to explore, As you enter one of the rooms, the door locks behind you! You find yourself locked in the Evil Queen Throne Room! You must find all of the clues in the room to escape before the Evil Queen returns and turns you into a statue. You only have 60 minutes!
